snippet.title: Legends of Boom - Trailer
snippet.description:
Legends of Boom is a fast-paced Card Battle game. Master the Path of Boom to upgrade your cards, then challenge opponents online with commentary by muppet sportscaster (voiced by NBA Jam announcer Tim Kitzrow) Flip Rimrod.

Wishlist today! Free on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3199930/Legends_of_Boom/
